1
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:57,440
Miss,

2
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,040
Once we cross this mountain,

3
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:00,920
we'll reach the villa Master left for you.

4
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:02,680
We can stay there for a few days.

5
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:07,160
Oh no.

6
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:08,610
Someone is here.

7
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:13,120
Stop! Run!

8
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:21,200
Don't run!

9
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,280
Stop!

10
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,050
Run, Miss! Xiaotao!

11
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:33,440
Come.

12
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:35,160
Go.

13
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:40,600
Xiaotao!

14
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,280
Miss!

15
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:43,960
Leave me!

16
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:49,000
Run, Miss!

17
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:50,160
Stay alive!

18
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:50,920
Xiaotao!

19
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,320
One wretched maid is dead.

20
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:03,320
There is one left.

21
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,480
Lord Xie ordered,

22
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,980
leave no one alive.

23
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,200
Miss,

24
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:50,440
you are

25
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:52,050
so beautiful today.

26
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,800
Even a fairy from heaven

27
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,360
couldn't compare to you.

28
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,960
When Young Master Xie...

29
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:57,800
Silly me.

30
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,320
I mean, your husband.

31
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:00,680
When your husband sees you...

32
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,680
They would definitely stare in awe.

33
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:04,640
Mother.

34
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,210
Today I am getting married.

35
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,140
The wedding dress I'm wearing

36
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:13,480
was designed by you yourself.

37
00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:16,320
If only you and Father

38
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,400
could see it.

39
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,420
What's that sound?

40
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,440
It makes me panic.

41
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:26,140
It's the sound of national mourning.

42
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:26,640
Oh no.

43
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:29,760
The country will have a great mourning.

44
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:32,840
Miss.

45
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,480
Something terrible has happened.

46
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:36,140
Bad news came from the palace.

47
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,760
The Emperor

48
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,200
has passed away.

49
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,000
Someone from the Xie family is here too.

50
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,060
But it's not the wedding procession.

51
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,500
A letter of annulment.

52
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,440
Is this Master Xie's idea,

53
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:53,040
or Xie Yuheng's?

54
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,440
Miss Yan,

55
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:56,000
my master says

56
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:58,280
that on the day of your wedding,

57
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:00,400
His Majesty passed away.

58
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:03,000
This is an ominous sign.

59
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:05,160
Now during the national mourning,

60
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,560
the whole country is grieving,

61
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,760
and all weddings and celebrations are strictly forbidden.

62
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,280
The Xie family has been loyal for generations

63
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,800
and has received imperial favor.

64
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:14,460
Thus, we dare not risk universal condemnation,

65
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:17,519
much less commit such treasonous acts.

66
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:20,680
Breaking off the engagement is truly out of helplessness,

67
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,680
but also our duty.

68
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:24,040
Please be understanding, Miss Yan.

69
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,200
Understanding?

70
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,960
The Xie family

71
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:32,240
publicly humiliated me on my wedding day,

72
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:35,640
trampling the dignity of me, Yan Qingshu,

73
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:38,480
and the Duke's Mansion under their feet.

74
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:41,250
And they still expect me to be understanding?

75
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:45,440
Sister, why are you so angry?

76
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,800
Butler Xie is right.

77
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:50,920
The Xie family is also thinking of the big picture,

78
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,880
and the safety of the entire household.

79
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,010
I will take my leave.

80
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,640
Have you forgotten, sister?

81
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,840
Your destiny is the 'Mars lingering in the Heart constellation'.

82
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:01,920
This was spoken by the Director of the Imperial Observatory himself.

83
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:04,720
Now, Father is missing,

84
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,920
and the primary wife passed away early.

85
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,440
Every single one of these things

86
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:09,640
has proven it.

87
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,680
You are getting married today,

88
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,360
and the Emperor suddenly passed away.

89
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:15,020
Such is your destiny, sister.

90
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,760
You really can't blame anyone else.

91
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:19,490
The 'Mars lingering in the Heart constellation'

92
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,320
was a rumor that you mother and daughter

93
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:24,120
deliberately spread back then.

94
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,720
Sister, how can you make such baseless accusations?

95
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,400
I truly mean well,

96
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,920
afraid that your obstinacy will anger the heavens

97
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:32,159
and implicate the entire Duke's estate.

98
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:33,920
Mother, quickly persuade her.

99
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,240
Qingshu,

100
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,400
do not be insolent.

101
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:41,000
The Xie family understands what's right and considers the overall situation.

102
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:43,880
This action does not fall short of etiquette in the slightest.

103
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,000
Today's matter

104
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:47,280
concerns the dignity of the entire clan.

105
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,800
I won't let you be insolent.

106
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,400
Somebody,

107
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,080
take this ignorant person

108
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:52,560
who bears an ominous destiny

109
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,000
and lock her back in her room.

110
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,440
And,

111
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,680
strip her of that eyesore of a red dress,

112
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,360
lest it clash with the national mourning

113
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,820
and bring disaster to the Duke Yan's estate.

114
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:05,520
I, Yan Qingshu, am the eldest legitimate daughter of the Duke's estate.

115
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:08,850
Let's see which impudent servant dares to lay a finger on me.

116
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,520
Lady Zhou.

117
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:12,440
How 'righteous' of you.

118
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:15,320
What an 'inauspicious fate'.

119
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:19,000
You just want to take advantage of my father's absence

120
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,440
to use the same vicious scheme you used on my mother

121
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,280
to wipe me out entirely, don't you?

122
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,140
Preposterous!

123
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:26,720
How dare you repeatedly slander your elders to their faces!

124
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,280
I'll tear your mouth apart!

125
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,040
Mother.

126
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,100
Calm down, Mother.

127
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,640
Sister must have been provoked

128
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:32,920
to speak so wildly.

129
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,440
Please don't let anger ruin your health, Mother.

130
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:35,900
Sister.

131
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,090
Hurry and apologize to her.

132
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,440
A concubine

133
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,840
wants me to apologize?

134
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:43,560
Can you

135
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,960
even bear it?

136
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,920
Drag her out immediately

137
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,480
and gag her!

138
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,159
No need.

139
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,180
I will walk out myself.

140
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:54,170
Since my father isn't here,

141
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:56,640
I don't want to stay in this house either.

142
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,040
Bah.

143
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:28,160
A jinx and a lowly slave.

144
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,180
Get out of here.

145
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:31,800
Don't dirty the grounds of our Duke's mansion.

146
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,200
Get lost.

147
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:04,010
Let's see where you can run.

148
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,600
Run.

149
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,800
Little lady, where else can you run?

150
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,260
Don't come closer.

151
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,380
Don't come closer.

152
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,300
Don't come closer.

153
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,860
Don't come closer.

154
00:08:58,880 --> 00:08:59,610
Where is she?

155
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,400
Get more men and keep searching.

156
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,720
We can't let her escape.

157
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,240
Yes.

158
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,840
How dare you try to stop us.

159
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,760
Leave immediately,

160
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:31,120
or you will die.

161
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,680
Just the two of you?

162
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,360
Uncle Zhao.

163
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:05,400
Uncle Zhao.

164
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,320
Uncle Zhao.

165
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:33,400
Duke.

166
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,440
Northern Border.

167
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,560
Xiao family.

168
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,720
Xie Yuheng.

169
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,600
Yan Mingli.

170
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,040
Lady Zhou.

171
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,200
Today,

172
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,360
you humiliate me,

173
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:03,920
exile me,

174
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:07,640
and try to wipe me out.

175
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:16,440
I, Yan Qingshu, swear to heaven,

176
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:21,400
even if my soul falls to the underworld,

177
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:26,280
I will crawl out of the bloody hell

178
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:28,160
to claim your lives.

179
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:33,080
I will make you pay in blood.

180
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:08,840
Yan Qingshu, you're finally here.

181
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:10,720
Who are you?

182
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:13,760
Why are you injured in this wilderness?

183
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,920
If you want to take my life,

184
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:20,040
now is the best time.

185
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:26,410
I'm not interested in killing.

186
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:29,080
But if you are determined to die,

187
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:31,720
I wouldn't mind sending you on your way.

188
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:00,800
Cuimei.

189
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,640
Cuimei.

190
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:04,840
Huachao.

191
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,840
Weikun, Huachao.

192
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:09,320
Long, Cong, Biao, Hao.

193
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:13,440
Shuang, Bin.

194
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,040
Ningzheng.

195
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:14,700
Ningzheng.

196
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:18,400
Hao, Chun, Kang, Shuai, Hua.

197
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:22,920
Weichao.

198
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,960
Qiang, Yuan, Liang, Bo.

199
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:41,240
Xi.

200
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,400
Xi.

201
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,360
Tao, Qiang.

202
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,600
Hui, Yue, Yun, Qing.

203
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,840
Yiyi.

204
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:01,840
Sisi.
